Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.90,0:01:03.66,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,地球的船 是军舰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:04.84,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:07.16,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,到底发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:10.10,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,住手 他是我们的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.25,0:01:43.49,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,大家来帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:45.50,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,亚瑟你们也去帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:51.96,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,阻隔在那个人与大家中间的坚冰终于融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:54.27,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,好了英二 不要反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.75,0:01:57.38,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,亚瑟 把英二的鞋脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.79,0:01:59.65,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,不要再挣扎了 英二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.54,0:02:05.03,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,但是 古拉多斯的威胁并没有因此消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:13.80,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,大卫 罗安 还有亚瑟都被卷入这场战争中了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:20.75,Layzner_Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,760)}地球的船来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:35.51,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:40.37,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,做得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:42.05,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,大家都没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:44.91,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,再差一点就要被干掉了 真是让人捏了一把汗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:48.07,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,本来还想好好教训一下的 却被他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:52.43,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,大卫 你对操纵还不熟 不要乱来 知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:53.64,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:56.70,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,罗安 你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:03:00.01,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,手终于不抖了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:03.94,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,什么啊 原来你吓成这样 可是你操纵的很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:06.16,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,去里面休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:08.56,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,等 等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:13.89,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,别生气 我不小心说溜嘴而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:18.91,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,话说回来 为什么敌人会终止攻击呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:20.25,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:27.20,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,说不定哪一天 敌人再进攻的时候也许只有祈祷的份了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.53,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白博士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:44.88,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,真的接通通信了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:48.32,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,对 有从美军基地来的通信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:49.44,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,从哪里发出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:53.12,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,不知道 杂音太大了 可是我真的有听到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:55.16,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,得救了 他们来救我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:57.56,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,有可能会被敌人先收到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:03:59.55,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,要赶快捕捉这条通信电波
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.96,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:04.69,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,这么说 干扰电波已经解除了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:07.42,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,古拉多斯的母舰移动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:09.16,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,母舰移动了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:12.70,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,说不定已经开始对地球的攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:15.48,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,这里是无人观测基地 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:18.31,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,这里是无人观测基地 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:20.30,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,这里是无人观测基地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:25.73,Default_Sub,Man A,0,0,0,,队长 这是接近中的飞行物体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:29.64,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,好像是地球的船 用电脑分析一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:30.34,Default_Sub,Man A,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:32.34,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,盖尔中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:36.26,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,卡露拉少尉 主雷达捕捉到了地球的船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:38.66,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,地球的船 是军舰吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:40.27,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:43.44,Default_Sub,Man A,0,0,0,,那船很明显是朝火星来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:46.60,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,听到了吗 马上接近那艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.60,0:04:49.16,Default_Sub,Eygle,0,0,0,,了解 请告诉我方位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:50.98,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,在12号位置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:55.06,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,推测需要时间15.02±0.01秒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:56.74,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,不过这是以我这的雷达为准
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:58.87,Default_Sub,Eygle,0,0,0,,了解 全机向该船前进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:04:59.67,Default_Sub,Pilots,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.81,0:05:10.97,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,他们的目的 我一定会给他们超出预期的结果的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.46,0:05:27.07,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,请回答 火星基地 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:28.13,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:35.89,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,这里是美国太空舰队定期运输船阿斯洛托法克二号 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:36.88,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:41.77,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,这里是美国太空舰队定期运输船阿斯洛托法克二号 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:44.42,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,美军的船来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:45.68,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:47.18,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我们能回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:49.05,Default_Sub,Man,0,0,0,,有人吗 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:50.14,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:53.74,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,这里是火星基地 阿斯洛托法克二号 听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:58.25,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,这里是火星基地 我是联合国的伊丽莎白博士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:00.29,Default_Sub,Man B,0,0,0,,联络上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:00.99,Default_Sub,Man C,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:01.99,Default_Sub,Man D,0,0,0,,好像是个女的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:06.65,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,我是罗吉亚大尉 伊丽莎白博士 你是火星的女神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:10.84,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,好性感的声音 你应该是金发碧眼对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:11.70,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,罗吉亚大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:14.01,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,真想马上飞到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:18.72,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,不要再开玩笑 有很多死者的灵魂在听你说话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:20.26,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,很多死者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:22.82,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,换我来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:26.74,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我是队长丹尼少佐 我想问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:31.20,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我们的基地跟苏联基地都没反应 到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:35.44,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,美苏基地因为双方的核弹在一瞬间毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.53,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,你说什么 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.92,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,是真的 两个基地都毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.45,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,一定是苏联的错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:42.78,Default_Sub,Man B,0,0,0,,又来挑衅了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:45.74,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,不是这样的 起因是因为外星人的介入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:48.70,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,谁的介入？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:53.08,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,是别的星球来的生命体 也就是外星人的介入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:53.98,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:54.85,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,说什么傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:05.79,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,虽然很难令人相信 但这是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:10.30,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白博士 马上请他们戒备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:15.24,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,他们会停止对我们的攻击 说不定是探测到地球的船了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:20.81,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,丹尼少佐 外星人可能已经探测到你们的船了 请马上戒备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:22.25,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:25.38,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我们虽然是运输舰 但也还是有武装的军舰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:26.93,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:28.39,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,请继续报告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:31.02,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,现在我们也被外星人盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:35.42,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,存活下来的只有我和参加太空体验计划的少年五人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:37.86,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,不 包括英二共六人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:39.64,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,英二 他是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:41.54,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,他是地球人跟外星人的混血儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:45.03,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,混血
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:47.56,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,现在没时间解释 之后慢慢说明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:50.71,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,丹尼少佐 请马上来救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:52.25,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我知道了 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:57.63,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,成功了 可以回地球了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:01.88,Default_Sub_Top,Arthur,0,0,0,,每天都看这个 我都看烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:05.16,Default_Sub_Top,Arthur,0,0,0,,可以不用一直看这边红色的天空了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:01.74,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,英二呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:03.00,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:04.17,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,出去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:06.19,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:08.01,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,这样终于能回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:12.01,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,告诉我地球的船的位置跟情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:15.54,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,已完成 在05号位置 好像要进入大气层
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:18.72,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,预测接触时间最少也要六秒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:19.42,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:30.92,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,已探测到目标
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:33.22,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,在02号位置 准备进入第三区域
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:36.87,Default_Sub,Roger?,0,0,0,,他说外星人的混血 她脑子是不是有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:39.42,Default_Sub,A,0,0,0,,那叫宇宙精神综合征
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:42.35,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,总之 有发生异状是没错的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:45.18,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,因为该异状让我军跟其他基地都失去消息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:48.74,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我搭航天飞机去确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:51.88,Default_Sub,B,0,0,0,,队长 马上进入N62轨道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:54.16,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我知道了 我搭航天飞机去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:55.55,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,你们的位置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:58.46,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,离美军基地很近的无人观测基地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:09:01.66,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,了解 那等会见 请保持通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:02.59,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:07.21,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,太好了 可以安心了 大家回地球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:10.01,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,奇怪 大卫他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:13.21,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,你到现在才发现啊 你好迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:16.27,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,他们一定是要去保护地球的军舰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:20.35,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,可是他们去的话 一定会被当成敌人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:22.52,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,这里是阿斯洛托法克二号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:23.22,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:25.43,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,现在丹尼少佐搭太空船去救你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:29.00,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,我知道了 你们可以跟地球或月球联络对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:29.99,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:33.95,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,请马上帮我跟他们联络 外星人准备要攻打地球了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:36.60,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,攻击地球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:39.74,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,她好像被男友甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:43.03,Default_Sub,B,0,0,0,,老跟小孩在一起会变得欲求不满的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:45.18,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,请马上把这警告传出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:47.10,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,罗吉亚 航天飞机待命中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.80,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,了解 马上打开舱门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:50.09,Default_Sub,C,0,0,0,,舱门锁解除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:02.51,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,那是什么 罗吉亚 看一下雷达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:03.29,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:06.49,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,二点钟方向 不 是你的一点四十分钟方向
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:07.45,Default_Sub,B,0,0,0,,是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:08.66,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,把它放大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:10.33,Default_Sub,B,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:11.81,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,不能再放大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:13.26,Default_Sub,C,0,0,0,,那是什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:14.60,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,是机器人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:22.31,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,博士 有SPT正接近地球的船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:23.57,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,请警告他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:28.46,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,罗吉亚大尉 外星人的机动部队接近中 请马上进行防卫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:31.04,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,我们已经确认目标了 交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:37.09,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,没问题 没问题的 他们是职业军人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:40.92,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,可是火星的军事基地还不是打不赢他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:44.57,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,那是 那是他们太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:49.26,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,阿修 达尔 你们两个先跟着那架小航天飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:51.03,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,在接到新的命令前先待命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:51.73,Default_Sub,All,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:55.01,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,其他人散开 在Alpha Shift展开包围
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:57.00,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,从各角度用雷达侦测情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:57.96,Default_Sub,All,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:11:01.23,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,丹尼少佐 敌人好像要散开再包围我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:06.92,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,准备攻击 不要让他们过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:18.87,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.69,0:11:23.71,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:26.54,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:30.82,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,他们到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:37.09,Default_Sub,Ash,0,0,0,,好迟钝的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:39.09,Default_Sub,Derro,0,0,0,,到底猴子就是猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:40.86,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,有SPT快速接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:41.56,Default_Sub,Derro,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:45.13,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,怎么了 又来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.91,Default_Sub,Derro,0,0,0,,那是 雷兹纳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:22.05,Default_Sub,Derro,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.05,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,背后受到攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:30.17,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,又来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:33.02,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,快一点 先去保护航天飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:39.62,Default_Sub,Derro,0,0,0,,阿修 先回去跟本队汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:40.36,Default_Sub,Ash,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:50.53,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,这里是丹尼 敌人有五架
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:52.72,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,但不知为何其中三架和其他两架打起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:54.05,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,少佐 你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:56.82,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我没事 总之进入备战状态
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:12:59.15,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,了解 以备战状态待机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:06.94,Default_Sub,B,0,0,0,,第一炮塔 第一号舰炮准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.11,0:13:09.99,Default_Sub,C,0,0,0,,第二号舰炮准备 导弹发射准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:12.15,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,还没 敌人还没动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:14.13,Default_Sub,A,0,0,0,,我们这里早就准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:17.03,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,他们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:25.26,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,目标是中型运输机 引擎是HYPERGOLIC LRD
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:29.32,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,武器有六门激光炮 还配备有导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:30.33,Default_Sub,Dal,0,0,0,,卡露拉少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:31.22,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:35.37,Default_Sub,Dal,0,0,0,,这样看来好像没有可以跟我们匹敌的武器 请交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:39.77,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,达尔军曹 我们要遵从雷达的指示 继续保护Alpha Shift
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:40.66,Default_Sub,Dal,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:46.74,Default_Sub,Dal,0,0,0,,切 你只会听盖尔队长的命令 对那些猴子也太谨慎了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:53.11,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,敌人开始行动了 要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:03.58,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,不要慌 敌人进入R12到R14地区 准备射击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:04.51,Default_Sub,???,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:05.56,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,攻击开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:08.06,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,是谁违反了命令 快离开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:11.01,Default_Sub,Dal,0,0,0,,没什么 我只是直接用雷达接收情报而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:13.83,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,导弹接近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:25.07,Default_Sub,Dal,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:31.95,Default_Sub,B,0,0,0,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:33.30,Default_Sub,C,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:36.71,Default_Sub,B,0,0,0,,尝尝这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:44.32,Default_Sub,Dal,0,0,0,,这是早期的激光嘛 威力只有我们的六分之一嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:47.34,Default_Sub,B,0,0,0,,激光也没用 而且他的速度好快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:49.24,Default_Sub,C,0,0,0,,导弹也被他打掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:51.88,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,直接攻击就行了 交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:55.18,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,看着吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:59.52,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,达尔军曹 雷达也捕捉到足够的资料了 快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:02.53,Default_Sub,Dal,0,0,0,,这些玩具 看我来干掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:04.26,Default_Sub,Dal,0,0,0,,机关部在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:12.90,Default_Sub,Dal,0,0,0,,在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:14.50,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,SPT接近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:16.34,Default_Sub,Dal,0,0,0,,阿修吗 快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:18.70,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,射击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:23.19,Default_Sub,Dal,0,0,0,,怎么会被这种东西打败呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:25.07,Default_Sub,Dal,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:31.18,Default_Sub,???,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:33.75,Default_Sub,C,0,0,0,,直接攻击的话就有效了 好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:38.17,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,达尔军曹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:40.53,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,全机 准备攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:43.07,Default_Sub,A,0,0,0,,卡露拉少尉 是之前那三架SPT
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:44.06,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,雷兹纳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:45.28,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,全机停止攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.52,0:15:49.55,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,请等一下盖尔中尉 请让我下达攻击命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:53.48,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,我们被击落一机 破损一机 不容许你乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:54.49,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,盖尔中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:58.81,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,, 快回来 先进行全资料分析 这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:03.60,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,了解 马上就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:07.03,Default_Sub,Egyle,0,0,0,,全机撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:14.42,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,罗安 追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:15.28,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.40,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,停下 不要太深入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:21.74,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,导弹接近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.74,0:16:28.07,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,快住手 停止攻击 我是你们这边的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:32.20,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我不是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:36.66,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,快住手 他是我方的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:38.04,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:43.00,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,没办法 大卫 罗安 撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:48.94,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,航天飞机应该降落了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:51.26,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,停 再射下去只是浪费子弹而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:55.14,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,丹尼少佐 没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:57.50,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,太惨了 这里太惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:17:01.65,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我们的基地只剩一个大坑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:06.98,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,什么都没有 一样东西都没留下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:10.97,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,那么 他说的都是真的咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:12.51,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:19.47,Default_Sub,Roger,0,0,0,,外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:32.70,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,欢迎你来 丹尼少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:34.49,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,我是伊丽莎白 这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:39.73,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我刚看到基地的遗迹了 真让人难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:42.50,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,你看到的都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:45.40,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,除了现在看到的这些人之外 其他人都死了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:48.59,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,还有两个小孩跟英二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:50.79,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,你刚说他是外星人是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:53.46,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,他为了保护我们而一直在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:57.66,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,他是我们的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:02.21,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,为了告诉我们地球的危机 从他的母星逃了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.78,0:18:13.88,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我们在这撑好久了 接下来可以好好睡一觉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:18.43,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,因为干扰电波 到目前为止我们都无法联络上月球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:21.06,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,是否可以请您跟地球联络呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.51,0:18:31.19,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:33.70,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,英二 阿尔巴特洛·英二·飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:37.02,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,OK 英二 我要把你当俘虏监禁起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:38.54,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,丹尼少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.37,0:18:44.44,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我们美军的调查队已从月球出发来这的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:47.25,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,那就是有援军来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:48.15,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.65,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,谁来用这胶带把他的手绑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:18:58.08,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,嘿 你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:18:59.53,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,我叫罗安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:00.44,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,把他绑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:04.95,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,英二是个有勇气并来告诉我们地球危机的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:08.01,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,还有 我们能得救也是因为他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:10.64,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,笨蛋 他是敌人派来的卧底
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:11.75,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,他不是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:18.02,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,还真像联合国的作风 但这样只会救了敌人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:19.61,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,我不允许你绑他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:21.92,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,谁听你的 把手伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:27.47,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,我不是开玩笑 反抗的话我会射死你的 不想死就伸手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:31.13,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,像你这样的人地球有很多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:31.87,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:35.61,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,什么都要用武力解决 真是野蛮的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:43.15,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,你的同伴也杀了地球人 你没有资格说我野蛮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:45.74,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:48.81,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,够了 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:52.28,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,你 给我让开 我要杀人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:54.11,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,我不会让你杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:56.13,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,你们是被洗脑了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:58.86,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,我们有自己的判断力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:05.75,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,你们是被吓怕了是吗 给我乖乖的走开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:08.46,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,不行 英二是我们的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:13.54,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,喂 亚瑟 你站在哪一边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:22.80,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,真疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:25.02,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,把枪收起来吧 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:28.57,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,好吧 暂时算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:31.88,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,大家先上航天飞机再搭船回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:33.15,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,现在搭船太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:38.23,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,外星人已被我们的导弹击退 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:39.48,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:43.56,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,刚才明明就打下一架敌机 情报说剩下的都撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:49.16,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,他们会撤退 是要整合大批武力再度攻击 接下来的攻击恐怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:50.16,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,不要小看地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:51.55,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,这是我冷静的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:53.54,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,可是援军也来了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:57.13,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,没错 不要浪费时间了 伊丽莎白博士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:20:58.70,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:21:02.09,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,大家 终于有机会回地球了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:04.67,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,博士 现在上船真的很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:08.21,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,他们一定会展开攻击的 不要上船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.34,0:21:12.93,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,大家怎么了 这是回地球的机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:15.21,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,大家应该早就有要冒险的觉悟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:17.47,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,还有我们军人在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:19.85,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,走吧 一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.91,0:21:21.31,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白博士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.39,0:21:24.35,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,丹尼少佐 我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.35,0:21:26.11,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,我要跟英二留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:27.39,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:30.45,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,我现在就死还太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:32.87,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,我也不要上船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:34.62,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,我也要留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:37.46,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,好 那就不妥协了 我在航天飞机上等你们五分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:43.03,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,回去吧 援军马上就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:46.42,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,好不好 西蒙尼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.42,0:21:50.46,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,不用客气了 亚瑟 再见 请你保重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.05,0:21:53.63,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:58.86,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我 我也相信英二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.02,0:22:01.69,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,可是 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:14.24,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,他要走了 这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.17,0:22:19.84,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,这些小鬼们到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.51,0:22:34.67,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,大家都选了英二 在生死之间做了重大的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.46,0:22:41.05,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,不 是大家把英二当同伴 相信同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.82,0:22:47.90,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,我 此时的我感觉想大叫 想大哭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.78,0:24:00.11,Default_Sub,Carks,0,0,0,,有时因为时间跟地点必须有舍命的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.61,0:24:02.60,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,我们要走 就表示英二也要一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.05,0:24:04.35,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,走吧 少佐
Dialogue: 1,0:24:04.44,0:24:08.61,Layzner_Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs150\pos(720,790)}再见 红色之星
